Class ExtendedModella

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.svvrl.goal.core.AbstractAlgorithm

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.EventListener, Algorithm, AlgorithmListener, ControllableAlgorithm, EditableAlgorithm, Translator<LTL,FSA>

    public class ExtendedModella
extends Modella
    This class provides an implementation of an extended MoDeLLa translation algorithm. The extension allows translation of formulae containing past operators.
    Author:
    Ming-Hsien Tsai
